reviews.text: Tasty fresh ingredients and good service.  My favourite place.

The food is good. This should be one of the best fast food restaurant in tuen mun ferry pier. MX is much better than cafe de coral as there are more new dishes to choose from. There are udon, chicken rice, curry, siu mei, etc. They don’t tastes really good but at least they are decent enough for such prices. And the environment here is quite chic and that’s one of the reasons why I like MX.
